idth: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/searching-for-content-across-platforms-on-google-tv.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/searching-for-content-across-platforms-on-google-tv.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/searching-for-content-across-platforms-on-google-tv.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/searching-for-content-across-platforms-on-google-tv.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/searching-for-content-across-platforms-on-google-tv.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/searching-for-content-across-platforms-on-google-tv.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Searching for content across platforms on Google TV\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/searching-for-content-across-platforms-on-google-tv.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/searching-for-content-across-platforms-on-google-tv.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWith the release of Google TV, a new refined interface built on Android TV, the platform\u0026#39;s experience has never been better. Google TV provides a sleek, modern interface that prioritizes personalization and makes it easy to find content.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eGoogle TV adds recommendations by showcasing content from different apps on the Home Screen. So, instead of browsing for content in individual apps, you can jump straight into the content from the Home Screen.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIt also provides a universal search button for finding content across different apps. For more information, check out our in-depth article on the \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/android-tv-google-tv-differences/#what-changes-does-google-tv-bring\" target=\"_blank\"\u003edifferences between Android TV and Google TV\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"best-voice-assistant-support\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e5 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Best Voice Assistant Support\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere are a handful of popular voice assistants, but Google Assistant is the best option on the market. Google Assistant is baked into Android TV by default. It offers seamless voice control that integrates deeply into the platform, enhancing user convenience and accessibility. Thanks to this, you can use it for hands-free control.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWhile the market offers a variety of \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-smart-tv-operating-system/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003esmart TV operating systems\u003c/a\u003e, Android TV stands out among the crowd due to its vibrant app ecosystem, ease of app installation on and off the Google Play Store, less bloatware, Google TV interface, and Google Assistant integration. Remember, you don\u0026#39;t need to buy a new TV to get Android TV. A streaming device like \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Google-Streamer-Streaming-Entertainment-Porcelain/dp/B0D8WJYSF9?tag=makeusw-20\u0026amp;ascsubtag=UUmuoUeUpU2035406\u0026amp;asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.makeuseof.com%2Fwhy-android-tv-best-smart-tv-platform%2F\u0026amp;asc_campaign=Evergreen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGoogle\u0026#39;s TV Streamer 4K\u003c/a\u003e is all you need.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
